info.title: ServiceBusManagementClient
info.description: Azure Service Bus client for managing Namespace, IPFilter Rules, VirtualNetworkRules and Zone Redundant

get.description: Lists all of the available ServiceBus REST API operations.

default.description: ServiceBus error response describing why the operation failed.
